<p>The pill style tries to be as informative as possible, so it
will show when picked fields were removed and when which were
newly added.  Checkbox Six has been removed, but was not selected
anyway, so silently ignored.</p>

<div id="cb_block" data-checkbox="cb" data-pick="one,two,four,five">
  <label for="cb_block" class="form-label">Pick some numbers</label>
  <div class="form-check">
    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="cb" value="one" id="cb_one">
    <label class="form-check-label" for="cb_one">One (picked)</label>
  </div>
  <div class="form-check">
    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="cb" value="two" id="cb_two">
    <label class="form-check-label" for="cb_two">Two (picked)</label>
  </div>
  <div class="form-check">
    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="cb" value="three" id="cb_three">
    <label class="form-check-label" for="cb_three">Three (not picked)</label>
  </div>
  <div class="form-check">
    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="cb" value="four" id="cb_four" disabled>
    <label class="form-check-label" for="cb_four">Four (picked, disabled)</label>
  </div>
  <div class="form-check" data-removed-in="20240101">
    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="cb" value="five" id="cb_five">
    <label class="form-check-label" for="cb_five">Five (removed, picked)</label>
  </div>
  <div class="form-check" data-removed-in="20240101">
    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="cb" value="six" id="cb_six">
    <label class="form-check-label" for="cb_six">Six (removed, not picked)</label>
  </div>
  <div class="form-check" data-added-in="20251010">
    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="cb" value="seven" id="cb_seven">
    <label class="form-check-label" for="cb_seven">Seven (added)</label>
  </div>
  <div class="form-check" data-added-in="20251010">
    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="cb" value="eight" id="cb_eight"
    required>
    <label class="form-check-label" for="cb_eight">Eight (added, required)</label>
  </div>
  <div class="change change-cb" for="cb_block" data-changed-in="20251010">
    Some numbers, and some were removed.
  </div>
</div>
